snippet.title: Clash of Aggression 0.5.2 - The Crusader
snippet.description:
New playable medieval character featured in version 0.5.2

Updated full version available for Windows, Mac and Linux at: https://mencapento.itch.io/clash-of-aggression and http://gamejolt.com/games/clash-of-aggression/193270

Clash of Aggression is all about "last stand": your team against dozens of enemies. It features characters and weapons from the middle ages and from modern times.
Online Co-op included!

Game built on Unity
